WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 13=

01:49.880 --> 01:51.440
Are you feeling better now?

02:12.464 --> 02:18.008
♪Love is not just romance♪

02:18.352 --> 02:21.681
♪They don't get my obsession♪

02:21.681 --> 02:23.401
My hands might be a bit cold.

02:23.401 --> 02:27.888
♪Why do two struggling souls make a vow♪

02:27.888 --> 02:30.672
♪And stake everything♪

02:31.801 --> 02:32.720
It's fine.

02:35.361 --> 02:36.440
Bear with it a little.

02:37.558 --> 02:41.880
♪Even with all these feelings,
we hold back♪

02:41.880 --> 02:43.281
You've been busy all day too.

02:43.961 --> 02:45.760
Why don't you rest early?

02:46.961 --> 02:48.241
I'm feeling much better now.

02:49.880 --> 02:51.160
It's only the second watch.

02:51.841 --> 02:55.760
In the latter half of the night,
your pain will be harder to bear.

02:56.440 --> 02:59.361
Master Helai taught me this technique.

02:59.841 --> 03:02.081
It penetrates the muscles
without harming the bones.

03:02.200 --> 03:03.720
A massage will ease you somehow.

03:04.330 --> 03:07.984
♪Or the green branch offered as a tutor♪

03:07.984 --> 03:11.884
♪Like friends
always standing side by side♪

03:11.884 --> 03:15.660
♪Love is but a beginning,
knowing each other day and night♪

03:15.660 --> 03:20.812
♪On such a long road,
holding hands and never letting go♪

03:22.124 --> 03:25.772
♪Only then do we understand why love♪

03:25.772 --> 03:30.540
♪Means more than one thing♪

03:31.664 --> 03:35.216
♪Love has never been just this,
I hope you know♪

03:35.216 --> 03:37.648
♪Even if we were once stubborn♪

03:37.648 --> 03:40.016
♪We understand when we trade places♪

03:40.016 --> 03:43.588
♪Gentleness hides in reserve♪

03:43.588 --> 03:46.281
♪Peacefully supporting
each other in silence♪

03:46.281 --> 03:49.880
Apply this poultice. You should
feel more comfortable tonight.

03:50.928 --> 03:54.616
♪Love is but a beginning,
the pain is brief♪

03:54.616 --> 04:00.081
♪On such a long road,
I hold your fingers♪

04:00.081 --> 04:00.920
Are you leaving?

04:01.801 --> 04:03.320
I'll stay with you a while longer.

04:09.920 --> 04:10.720
Are you cold?

04:13.361 --> 04:14.281
A little.

04:17.880 --> 04:18.921
Come up here.

04:24.440 --> 04:26.440
It rains a lot lately.
The nights are chilly.

04:26.801 --> 04:27.880
I'm worried you'd...

04:59.200 --> 05:00.161
It's so warm.

05:04.121 --> 05:07.041
Actually, I like sneezing.

05:09.721 --> 05:10.520
Why?

05:11.520 --> 05:14.760
Because it means
someone is thinking of me,

05:15.041 --> 05:16.161
and someone misses me.

05:17.840 --> 05:18.880
That's nonsense.

05:26.280 --> 05:27.161
Mo Xiuyao,

05:29.041 --> 05:30.161
do you have a nickname?

05:32.921 --> 05:35.561
Take me, for example. I'm Ye Li.

05:36.001 --> 05:38.640
People close to me call me Li.

05:39.080 --> 05:40.640
I've always called you Your Highness.

05:40.880 --> 05:42.320
Sometimes I call you by your name.

05:43.200 --> 05:45.960
It feels distant
and makes us seem distant.

05:48.241 --> 05:51.161
My parents used to call me Yao.

05:53.440 --> 05:55.880
My brother and sister-in-law
also called me that.

05:56.481 --> 05:57.760
Then I'll call you that too.

05:58.161 --> 05:58.960
Okay.

06:01.280 --> 06:02.080
Yao.

06:05.880 --> 06:08.400
Yao, Yao.

06:09.801 --> 06:11.640
Yao, Yao.

06:14.280 --> 06:15.241
I hear you.

06:27.200 --> 06:28.001
Yao,

06:30.121 --> 06:31.840
have I ever told you?

06:33.361 --> 06:34.561
This time down the mountain,

06:35.721 --> 06:37.520
I have so many things to do.

06:39.280 --> 06:40.561
What things?

06:45.280 --> 06:47.241
I want to eat lots of good food.

06:48.681 --> 06:51.640
I want to take back my mom's shop.

06:53.400 --> 06:55.080
I also want to find my seniors.

06:57.080 --> 06:57.880
And also...

06:59.601 --> 07:01.440
Help that senior chop down a tree?

07:04.921 --> 07:06.280
It's already done.

07:09.001 --> 07:10.561
And help you stand up

07:12.121 --> 07:13.640
and make you live happily.

07:54.400 --> 07:55.200
Your Highness,

07:57.121 --> 07:58.121
a decree from the palace.

08:01.280 --> 08:02.400
Greetings, Your Highness.

08:03.400 --> 08:06.960
The Empress Dowager summons
Your Highness to the palace.

08:22.320 --> 08:24.161
A few days ago, I heard

08:24.601 --> 08:26.721
that Princess Ding had an accident
and was injured.

08:27.320 --> 08:28.760
Is she well now?

08:28.880 --> 08:29.960
Thank you for your concern.

08:30.121 --> 08:31.921
My wife is fine now.

08:32.721 --> 08:33.560
That's good.

08:33.920 --> 08:35.400
If there is still any discomfort,

08:35.520 --> 08:38.321
you can summon an imperial physician
to your mansion for treatment.

08:38.680 --> 08:41.361
It's also a good opportunity
to examine your legs.

08:41.920 --> 08:44.280
That girl, still injured herself,

08:44.280 --> 08:46.361
yet has already arranged
to treat your legs.

08:47.160 --> 08:50.441
Such a trivial family matter
has actually reached your ears.

08:51.560 --> 08:54.001
Your leg treatment is a major event.

08:54.280 --> 08:55.920
How could I possibly not know?

08:58.001 --> 08:59.121
Thank you for your concern.

09:00.601 --> 09:05.001
May I ask why Your Majesty
has summoned me today?

09:06.920 --> 09:09.841
There is indeed one matter, an old case.

09:10.601 --> 09:13.721
You are aware of the previous
assassination of Yuan Fang.

09:14.481 --> 09:19.201
Yuan Fang, a key official,
was killed on the capital's outskirts?

09:19.640 --> 09:23.400
I absolutely do not believe
it was done by roving bandits.

09:23.520 --> 09:24.721
I also know

09:24.760 --> 09:27.201
there's much talk
in and out of court lately,

09:27.201 --> 09:29.721
all pointing to Marquis Muyang's
involvement in this case.

09:30.321 --> 09:31.640
What is your opinion?

09:34.721 --> 09:37.160
Court affairs are like chess in the fog.

09:38.160 --> 09:41.680
Black and white pieces
are both hidden under thick fog.

09:42.040 --> 09:45.121
But the player always
has their own strategy.

09:46.601 --> 09:50.560
In my view, Military Governor Yuan's
case involves many parties.

09:51.601 --> 09:52.601
Ultimately,

09:53.280 --> 09:56.361
someone always stands
to benefit from it.

09:56.400 --> 09:59.241
Yuan Fang was an honest official
with clean hands.

09:59.721 --> 10:02.880
This time, to investigate
the weaponry case,

10:02.880 --> 10:04.040
he traveled far to Huaixi

10:04.040 --> 10:05.361
and exhausted all his efforts.

10:06.280 --> 10:07.760
The death of such a loyal official

10:08.160 --> 10:12.601
not only grieves me
but also shakes the entire court.

10:13.081 --> 10:17.520
Now, I entrust this case to you
to supervise with full authority.

10:18.201 --> 10:20.520
His Majesty trusts you, and so do I.

10:20.560 --> 10:23.800
Remember, no matter who is implicated,

10:24.560 --> 10:27.441
I want the truth to be revealed.

10:29.560 --> 10:31.481
I accept the order.

10:35.152 --> 10:38.416
(Ye Mansion)

10:44.601 --> 10:46.481
My lord, have some medicine.

10:50.920 --> 10:53.280
You were fine.
What's been going on these days?

10:55.481 --> 10:56.481
She's coming.

10:57.961 --> 10:58.961
She's coming.

10:58.961 --> 11:01.160
Who? Who's coming?

11:26.841 --> 11:28.361
If you ask when you'll meet again,

11:29.001 --> 11:32.121
it's only in dreams at the third watch.

11:32.760 --> 11:35.361
This person is no longer alive.

11:44.321 --> 11:46.961
The Empress Dowager orders
to investigate Yuan Fang's death?

11:48.160 --> 11:49.760
Marquis Muyang didn't do it?

11:50.680 --> 11:53.321
Marquis Muyang has been
particularly domineering these years.

11:53.321 --> 11:55.001
He's drifted from the Empress Dowager.

11:55.001 --> 11:58.520
Their relationship is no longer one
of complete trust.

11:58.560 --> 12:01.841
In any case, the investigation
is no bad thing for us.

12:01.920 --> 12:04.040
Handle it discreetly.
Don't alert the enemy.

12:04.520 --> 12:07.721
Contact Scribe Gu if you need
assistance from Jingzhao Prefecture.

12:09.800 --> 12:13.961
Yuan Fang's case is rife with doubt.
Hidden secrets likely lurk behind it.

12:14.201 --> 12:16.441
Alright. I'm on it.

12:20.201 --> 12:21.481
That's all for Yuan Fang.

12:22.601 --> 12:23.920
Now let's talk about your legs.

12:24.441 --> 12:28.201
Why didn't you tell me
about such a big thing at the time?

12:30.201 --> 12:31.800
How is it? Does it still hurt?

12:31.800 --> 12:32.640
Much better.

12:34.800 --> 12:35.680
Good.

12:36.961 --> 12:38.400
Her Highness is the best.

12:38.601 --> 12:40.920
She found a way
to treat your legs so quickly.

12:41.280 --> 12:46.001
As your close friend for many years,
I'm truly ashamed.

12:46.001 --> 12:47.800
Leave. If you don't leave now,
I'll kick you.

12:47.800 --> 12:50.760
Alright, I'm going.
Take care and rest well.

12:51.400 --> 12:54.920
As long as it's getting better,
the suffering wasn't in vain.

12:56.920 --> 12:57.640
I'm off.

13:00.961 --> 13:03.560
I have a few more
Jingzhao Prefecture matters to report.

13:03.680 --> 13:04.481
Go ahead.

13:08.201 --> 13:10.961
The water-transported grain
deficit case is closed.

13:10.961 --> 13:13.961
The so-called grain warehouse rats
and flying thieves

13:13.961 --> 13:15.201
were all excuses.

13:15.201 --> 13:19.721
The water transport officials stuffed
reed tubes into the sacks at Ba Bridge.

13:19.721 --> 13:24.040
Then at Ba River's sharp bend,
they pretended to drop anchor and stop,

13:24.040 --> 13:25.441
claiming to worship the River God,

13:25.441 --> 13:27.560
but they used the river
to sneak the grain away.

13:27.880 --> 13:29.680
The old cases are almost all settled.

13:29.680 --> 13:31.760
There are a few new matters recently.

13:32.201 --> 13:34.920
Huaizhen Ward is far from the river,
so seven wells need to be dug.

13:34.920 --> 13:37.520
A fire broke out near Chang Tower,
burning down many residences.

13:37.520 --> 13:40.280
They need to be rebuilt.
But all this requires your funding.

13:46.760 --> 13:47.560
Continue.

13:47.760 --> 13:50.721
The household registration document
needs your personal review.

13:53.400 --> 13:55.400
Your Highness! Your Highness!

13:55.721 --> 13:56.760
You have a visitor.

13:56.800 --> 13:57.520
Who is it?

13:57.520 --> 13:58.721
Your father has come.

14:11.121 --> 14:12.361
Father, what brings you here?

14:16.121 --> 14:19.201
You've been married long
but skipped the homecoming visit.

14:19.560 --> 14:21.201
I just wanted to come and see you.

14:24.040 --> 14:28.560
In my two months back at the Ye mansion
from Lishan Mountain, I barely saw you.

14:29.201 --> 14:32.841
Now that I'm married,
you've actually remembered me.

14:34.481 --> 14:37.241
It was during the New Year holiday.
I was busy.

14:37.241 --> 14:38.961
What brings you here today?

14:41.241 --> 14:42.040
Actually,

14:44.081 --> 14:47.121
I came today to ask you something.

14:48.640 --> 14:51.081
How is your mom?

15:00.481 --> 15:01.321
My mom

15:03.121 --> 15:04.721
has been dead for eight years.

15:33.721 --> 15:34.441
Marquis Muyang.

15:38.361 --> 15:41.601
Guard Qin, you went to Cangbei
on Marquis Muyang's business.

15:41.640 --> 15:44.920
You were gone for three months.
It must have been tiring.

15:47.001 --> 15:48.841
Marquis Muyang, you look worried.

15:52.121 --> 15:55.040
Everyone suspects
I'm behind Yuan Fang's death.

15:55.121 --> 15:58.961
Bad luck clings to me.
Nothing goes my way.

16:04.241 --> 16:06.040
Are things smooth on your end?

16:07.001 --> 16:07.760
Yes.

16:08.040 --> 16:10.601
Cangbei is politically chaotic.
Crossbows are in high demand.

16:11.400 --> 16:14.841
You've worked hard.
Stay a while longer this time.

16:16.280 --> 16:17.081
Yes.

16:18.160 --> 16:24.241
Now, Lu Zhi, Chen Fenyuan, and Tian Feng
have been killed one after another.

16:25.760 --> 16:28.560
Even Lu Changfu
couldn't escape misfortune.

16:29.481 --> 16:30.280
Hengyuan.

16:31.280 --> 16:35.841
Over the years, I've seen
your dedication and hard work.

16:35.841 --> 16:37.121
(Qin Cang)

16:37.121 --> 16:40.601
However, while you can
handle court affairs,

16:40.841 --> 16:44.241
there are some matters
that require Qin Cang.

16:45.400 --> 16:49.280
You're farsighted, Marquis Muyang.
I am ashamed of my inadequacy.

16:51.961 --> 16:54.981
Father! Father! Fa...

16:55.441 --> 16:56.241
Young Lord.

16:56.880 --> 16:57.721
Guard Qin?

16:57.721 --> 16:58.520
Young Lord.

16:59.040 --> 17:00.121
You're back?

17:02.601 --> 17:03.880
It's been a few months.

17:05.641 --> 17:06.560
(Zhou Tianyang)
You've become fairer.

17:07.241 --> 17:08.241
And sturdier.

17:08.840 --> 17:11.520
I heard Father say you went home
to visit family. Well?

17:11.520 --> 17:12.840
Is everything well at home?

17:15.921 --> 17:18.001
Thank you for your concern. All is well.

17:18.360 --> 17:19.120
That's good.

17:19.641 --> 17:22.320
Father, look at the fish I caught.

17:23.241 --> 17:25.520
You little monkey,
you're covered in filth.

17:25.921 --> 17:28.241
You know what?
I went to the reed marshes today,

17:28.280 --> 17:30.520
set out three dou
of fermented grain and bran as bait,

17:30.520 --> 17:33.241
and caught two black carp, big and fat.

17:33.241 --> 17:34.352
Especially this first one.

17:34.721 --> 17:36.320
When I was jigging the float,

17:36.681 --> 17:38.161
once the rod tip touched the water,

17:38.280 --> 17:40.001
splash! The float sank right away!

17:40.001 --> 17:41.600
Tonight, let's have a whole fish feast.

17:42.080 --> 17:42.921
Alright, alright.

17:43.280 --> 17:45.241
Look at your nose, all dirty.

17:46.080 --> 17:47.881
Careful, or the fish demon will get you.

18:08.201 --> 18:09.080
Guard Qin.

18:10.641 --> 18:11.600
Guard Qin.

18:13.881 --> 18:14.840
Guard Qin.

18:16.040 --> 18:19.040
You'll be staying in the capital
long-term this time.

18:21.241 --> 18:24.241
You can't do without
a comfortable residence.

18:25.280 --> 18:28.600
I happen to have an old house
in the west of the city.

18:29.001 --> 18:32.401
It's a bit old, but well-preserved.

18:32.760 --> 18:35.441
It's a three-courtyard compound
in a good location

18:35.681 --> 18:37.840
and close to the marquis's residence.

18:39.441 --> 18:40.641
Thank you, Commissioner.

18:40.961 --> 18:44.441
But I've already found a place to stay,
so I won't trouble you.

18:45.320 --> 18:47.080
Guard Qin, wait for me.

18:49.120 --> 18:49.620
Young Lord.

18:51.201 --> 18:53.001
Guard Qin, you walk so fast.

18:54.961 --> 18:57.961
For some reason,
Father has suddenly become vegetarian.

18:58.001 --> 18:59.161
He won't even eat this fish.

18:59.401 --> 19:01.800
Since you're back in the capital
with nothing to do,

19:01.800 --> 19:03.840
why not stay and drink with me
at a pleasure house?

19:04.881 --> 19:07.241
I'm a bit exhausted
from the long journey.

19:08.600 --> 19:09.100
Very well.

19:10.401 --> 19:12.161
You are Father's favorite.

19:12.721 --> 19:15.001
Even I have to treat you
with some respect.

19:18.001 --> 19:19.001
Take this black carp.

19:21.881 --> 19:22.840
I don't like fish.

19:37.441 --> 19:40.961
That's perfect.
I happen to love fresh fish.

19:40.961 --> 19:43.481
Why not give this fish
to me instead, Young Lord?

19:47.401 --> 19:48.201
Alright.

19:55.161 --> 19:56.641
Thank you, Young Lord.

20:24.800 --> 20:25.600
My lord.

20:28.280 --> 20:29.080
My lord.

20:29.441 --> 20:33.080
No matter how urgent the matter,
you must take care of your health first.

20:33.520 --> 20:34.921
You haven't eaten for half a day.

20:40.840 --> 20:42.681
Where did the lord go today?

20:43.360 --> 20:46.560
My lady, the lord went
to Prince Ding's Mansion at noon.

21:19.161 --> 21:22.241
Don't come closer! Don't come closer!

21:26.921 --> 21:28.881
My lord, it's me. It's me.

21:29.201 --> 21:30.760
Don't be afraid. It's me.

21:31.241 --> 21:33.760
Don't be afraid. It's alright.

21:33.760 --> 21:35.472
Don't be afraid.

21:39.344 --> 21:40.080
It's alright.

21:57.360 --> 21:58.161
Play here.

21:59.320 --> 22:00.441
Don't speak.

22:00.441 --> 22:02.161
Listen to me. Play here.

22:04.921 --> 22:05.721
Here.

22:07.840 --> 22:09.481
Why did you play here, Mom?

22:10.280 --> 22:11.120
Are you sure?

22:11.921 --> 22:12.800
Can't I?

22:13.360 --> 22:15.961
If you play here,
this whole area will be lost.

22:16.560 --> 22:18.921
You should have listened to me
and played here.

22:19.560 --> 22:20.800
Here she loses even faster.

22:21.280 --> 22:22.080
See?

22:24.320 --> 22:25.120
Look.

22:25.721 --> 22:26.560
Stop playing.

22:27.080 --> 22:28.721
Mom, let's not play with her anymore.

22:29.040 --> 22:31.600
It's just chess.
You're quitting over one loss?

22:32.040 --> 22:34.961
Aunt, you're a monster.
Who would play with you?

22:35.360 --> 22:39.120
Wuyou, don't talk nonsense.
Our chess skills are not refined.

22:39.560 --> 22:42.001
You're quite good.
Let's play another round.

22:42.080 --> 22:42.881
Sure.

22:43.080 --> 22:44.721
What are you playing that's so lively?

22:44.721 --> 22:45.721
Yao, you're here.

22:46.260 --> 22:46.760
Uncle.

22:46.760 --> 22:47.840
We're playing chess.

22:47.840 --> 22:49.120
Li's chess skills are superb.

22:49.120 --> 22:50.921
Neither Wuyou nor I are a match for her.

22:52.080 --> 22:53.560
Do you want to give it a try?

22:54.080 --> 22:56.800
Uncle, don't try. She plays ferociously.

22:57.001 --> 22:57.881
Is that so?

22:59.921 --> 23:02.921
I didn't expect you
to be a chess master as well.

23:03.161 --> 23:05.280
No master. I just know a little.

23:05.560 --> 23:07.961
Yao hasn't played chess
in a long time either.

23:08.360 --> 23:11.560
Is that so? Then please instruct me,
Your Highness.

23:11.921 --> 23:13.520
Sure. Come on.

23:19.681 --> 23:20.560
Here?

23:23.161 --> 23:23.921
What?

23:24.881 --> 23:25.881
Won't you think it over?

23:27.961 --> 23:31.320
Just play. Why so much talk?

23:50.441 --> 23:53.481
I told you that Aunt is a monster.

23:53.721 --> 23:55.001
No one can beat her.

23:57.560 --> 23:58.560
Don't say that.

23:59.241 --> 24:01.681
His Highness
was just momentarily careless,

24:01.721 --> 24:03.161
allowing me to gain the upper hand.

24:04.641 --> 24:05.441
Again.

24:11.441 --> 24:13.401
Well, it's getting late.

24:13.641 --> 24:15.201
I'll go check on the kitchen first.

24:18.020 --> 24:18.520
Let's go.

24:18.520 --> 24:19.401
I'm not going.

24:19.401 --> 24:20.161
Hurry up and go.

24:20.360 --> 24:21.120
I want to stay.

24:21.120 --> 24:21.840
Move!

24:21.881 --> 24:23.441
I'll go prepare some tea and snacks.

24:23.600 --> 24:24.320
Stop watching.

24:25.681 --> 24:26.560
Your Highness, I...

24:26.560 --> 24:27.481
You're going too?

24:38.520 --> 24:40.360
You indeed have
extraordinary chess skills.

24:40.560 --> 24:42.520
Truly worthy of someone
from Lishan Academy.

24:44.641 --> 24:45.872
You flatter me, Your Highness.

24:46.161 --> 24:47.721
I was bored on the mountain.

24:48.721 --> 24:51.520
So I practiced by playing
against myself all day long.

24:54.921 --> 24:58.320
With so many people on Lishan Mountain,
why did you play chess with yourself?

25:00.161 --> 25:02.921
They thought my skills were poor
and wouldn't play with me.

25:19.721 --> 25:20.641
You know sword arts?

25:22.641 --> 25:23.441
What?

25:23.961 --> 25:25.800
Your move, hiding yin and yang
in the wrist,

25:26.161 --> 25:27.760
is from a masterful sword art.

25:28.921 --> 25:31.201
Me? A sword art?

25:33.120 --> 25:33.921
Give me your hand.

25:36.441 --> 25:39.241
A sword art focuses on thrusting,
with a flexible grip.

25:39.600 --> 25:41.080
Fingerwork controls the sword.

25:41.600 --> 25:44.360
Given the thick plum blossom calluses
on your thumb and index finger,

25:44.520 --> 25:47.241
you've practiced sword art
for a long time.

25:49.040 --> 25:50.441
There's such a nuance?

25:51.241 --> 25:55.040
Then what about saber practice?
Do calluses grow in different places?

25:55.641 --> 25:58.481
Saber arts slash and chop more.
The pressure points differ.

25:58.641 --> 26:01.360
So the calluses that form are different.

26:01.921 --> 26:05.040
I used to practice saber. My calluses
were all on the center of my palm.

26:12.800 --> 26:13.600
But there are none.

26:14.320 --> 26:15.641
It's long since I last practiced.

26:18.641 --> 26:21.800
So you know sword arts.
You know martial skills, right?

26:24.401 --> 26:25.760
You've guessed wrong.

26:26.241 --> 26:28.840
These calluses
aren't from sword practice.

26:28.840 --> 26:30.040
They're from manual labor.

26:30.360 --> 26:32.040
Lishan Academy was sealed
for eight years.

26:32.241 --> 26:35.001
We had to take care
of our own food and clothing.

26:35.040 --> 26:36.600
I had to plant vegetables and crops,

26:37.201 --> 26:38.320
weave cloth, pick tea,

26:38.441 --> 26:39.800
also chop firewood, hunt,

26:39.800 --> 26:41.001
sew, mend, and wash.

26:41.320 --> 26:42.441
There was so much work.

26:43.921 --> 26:47.241
There were many people on the mountain.
You had to do all the chores?

26:50.120 --> 26:51.840
The more people, the more work.

26:53.161 --> 26:55.001
Someone as noble as you
wouldn't understand.

27:03.120 --> 27:04.600
Your Highnesses,

27:04.600 --> 27:07.241
Ms. Wen says the meal is ready
and asks you to come eat.

27:07.641 --> 27:09.921
Your Highness,
Master Feng is here again.

27:22.201 --> 27:23.001
What is it?

27:25.441 --> 27:29.280
According to your orders,
I have indeed found something.

27:46.481 --> 27:48.840
Of course, I might have made a mistake.

27:49.241 --> 27:50.320
Three more days, perhaps?

27:50.320 --> 27:51.441
Hand it over.

27:55.360 --> 27:55.961
Give it to me.

28:23.001 --> 28:24.752
She hired those men
to assassinate herself?

28:25.721 --> 28:26.520
Yes.

28:28.441 --> 28:31.280
The person Her Highness hired
is Zheng Qin of the Red Scorpion Gang.

28:31.600 --> 28:33.241
He and Lu Changfu were close.

28:33.241 --> 28:35.681
He set fire to the seven scholars
of Lishan Mountain.

28:35.840 --> 28:38.441
Lishan Academy has a deep
blood feud with this man.

28:38.800 --> 28:39.800
Did Her Highness hire him

28:42.441 --> 28:44.760
because she tried
to use you to get rid of him?

28:50.320 --> 28:52.201
Truly killing two birds with one stone.

28:53.520 --> 28:54.320
Keep digging.

28:56.641 --> 28:57.441
Into what?

28:57.641 --> 28:58.681
One lie, all lies.

28:59.241 --> 29:01.401
Have you ever seen a liar
who tells only one lie?

29:04.641 --> 29:06.360
And now that I think carefully,

29:07.360 --> 29:10.641
many things have happened
since she came down the mountain.

29:11.441 --> 29:13.961
Lv Cheng lost his life
because of a name.

29:14.040 --> 29:17.040
Lu Changfu died in a blaze.

29:18.040 --> 29:20.760
Yuan Fang was rescued at Suixue Pass.

29:22.120 --> 29:27.401
All these people are intricately
connected to Lishan Academy.

29:29.360 --> 29:30.961
I think you're overthinking it.

29:32.441 --> 29:33.481
I'm overthinking?

29:36.120 --> 29:37.600
Heiyun Cavalry returned unapproved.

29:38.161 --> 29:39.360
Suixue Pass fell.

29:39.560 --> 29:42.001
My brother
was wrongly accused and killed.

29:43.441 --> 29:45.681
Which of these was not because
we didn't think enough?

29:47.441 --> 29:50.560
You, I, and my household

29:52.001 --> 29:53.441
are all walking a tightrope.

29:56.201 --> 30:00.401
One misstep and we'll fall
into an abyss of eternal damnation.

30:01.320 --> 30:04.040
Yet I can't even figure out
what my own wife is doing.

30:08.161 --> 30:09.241
How can I be at ease?

30:10.040 --> 30:10.800
Yes.

30:14.161 --> 30:18.360
Frankly, Her Highness
did handle this matter poorly.

30:19.641 --> 30:21.681
But her original intention
wasn't to harm you.

30:22.201 --> 30:23.641
Look, after such a big detour,

30:24.800 --> 30:27.040
wasn't she sincerely trying
to treat your legs?

30:28.921 --> 30:32.241
Whether it was sincere
remains to be seen.

30:48.441 --> 30:49.641
Has Feng Zhiyao not left yet?

30:50.040 --> 30:51.001
He has left.

31:03.441 --> 31:04.241
Your Highness.

31:04.441 --> 31:05.681
Is His Highness inside?

31:19.961 --> 31:21.201
Why aren't the lamps lit?

31:23.721 --> 31:25.600
The medicine is ready. Come take it.

31:29.840 --> 31:30.600
What's wrong?

31:40.201 --> 31:41.360
Have I wronged you?

31:46.800 --> 31:50.201
So, that day when we returned
from Zhengyi Temple,

31:50.681 --> 31:52.520
it was you who hired men
to kidnap yourself?

32:14.280 --> 32:17.040
No wonder they knew
our whereabouts so well.

32:17.921 --> 32:20.961
They had every advantage
but didn't strike hard.

32:21.600 --> 32:22.800
So it was you.

32:23.001 --> 32:27.080
I'm truly foolish. I never imagined
it would actually be you.

32:28.800 --> 32:31.840
Ye Li, why did you do that?

32:33.681 --> 32:35.600
Does Your Highness
not know why I did it?

32:38.120 --> 32:41.040
For me?

32:42.441 --> 32:43.441
Your Highness is clever.

32:48.800 --> 32:50.441
I was completely fooled by you.

32:51.320 --> 32:54.201
Those few days, I was so anxious
I couldn't eat or sleep.

32:55.201 --> 32:57.040
How can I be called clever?

32:57.840 --> 33:00.201
Your Highness's leg condition
has been neglected for years.

33:00.520 --> 33:03.840
I suggested it several times,
but you wouldn't let me try.

33:04.760 --> 33:07.241
I had no choice
but to push you a little.

33:08.921 --> 33:10.840
You really went to great lengths.

33:14.520 --> 33:17.481
Yao, I never intended to harm you.

33:21.201 --> 33:23.001
Indeed, it was for my own good.

33:24.600 --> 33:26.001
I, a cripple,

33:27.600 --> 33:30.040
a fallen noble stripped of power,

33:32.600 --> 33:37.441
am so honored to be favored
by a descendant of Lishan Academy.

33:38.320 --> 33:41.961
To heal my legs, you toiled and schemed,

33:42.360 --> 33:43.681
put yourself in danger,

33:44.441 --> 33:45.881
and gave me a rude awakening

33:46.800 --> 33:48.201
to bring me to my senses.

33:50.241 --> 33:51.961
How moving!

33:52.921 --> 33:54.600
And here I am, so ungrateful.

33:55.641 --> 33:57.961
I truly failed your painstaking efforts.

33:58.360 --> 33:59.441
Don't say that.

34:05.641 --> 34:07.560
Everyone knows about my brother's case.

34:08.921 --> 34:12.361
He received an imperial edict
and led his troops back to the capital.

34:13.841 --> 34:17.401
But when he arrived,
the late emperor had died.

34:19.321 --> 34:23.200
He was convicted of treason
and lost his life.

34:25.560 --> 34:28.680
But no one knows where
that imperial edict he received went.

34:30.321 --> 34:32.120
It was because
he trusted others too easily

34:32.321 --> 34:33.720
and handed over the edict,

34:33.720 --> 34:35.560
wanting to prove
he hadn't committed treason!

34:40.120 --> 34:42.200
And so he 'returned
to the capital without an edict'

34:44.961 --> 34:46.441
and was sentenced to death.

34:49.080 --> 34:49.881
Look,

34:53.481 --> 34:55.640
this is the consequence
of being gullible.

34:59.600 --> 35:00.520
I didn't lie to you.

35:10.841 --> 35:11.640
Jin!

35:35.520 --> 35:36.321
My lady.

35:41.720 --> 35:42.640
It's alright.

35:47.761 --> 35:48.801
It will be alright.

35:50.080 --> 35:53.520
(But what if the posthumous edict
is already destroyed?)

35:55.441 --> 35:59.040
(Then we will peel back
the truth layer by layer.)

36:35.120 --> 36:35.921
Your Highness.

36:48.680 --> 36:49.481
Your Highness?

36:51.560 --> 36:52.401
Your Highness?

36:59.481 --> 37:00.520
What time is it?

37:00.881 --> 37:02.080
A quarter past the Chen hour.

37:04.481 --> 37:05.361
Where is His Highness?

37:06.200 --> 37:07.240
In his room.

37:07.321 --> 37:08.481
Looks like he's off to work.

37:08.481 --> 37:09.560
Jin is attending to him.

37:10.560 --> 37:13.040
How can he go to the office
while still recovering?

37:14.321 --> 37:15.441
I don't know either.

37:16.961 --> 37:19.801
By the way, Your Highness,
today is Madam's birthday.

37:19.801 --> 37:21.321
The gifts are all prepared.

37:21.321 --> 37:22.801
Are we going back to the Ye Mansion?

37:25.801 --> 37:26.560
Yes, we are.

37:28.080 --> 37:29.001
Help me change.

37:29.640 --> 37:30.441
Yes.

37:40.600 --> 37:41.801
(Let me down!)

37:42.401 --> 37:43.441
I'm here to save you.

37:43.761 --> 37:46.321
If you fall,
I can't do anything about it.

37:49.001 --> 37:50.841
Young General, they're trying to escape!

37:52.120 --> 37:54.680
In their dreams!
None of them will escape!

37:54.761 --> 37:55.481
After them!

37:55.481 --> 37:56.001
Yes!

37:57.801 --> 38:01.441
As the Chief Garrison Commander,
how could you act so recklessly?

38:02.001 --> 38:05.040
Should I have watched desert bandits
slaughter innocent merchants?

38:05.321 --> 38:06.481
You could've reported to me.

38:06.600 --> 38:09.560
By the time you arrived, those people
would probably have been dead.

38:12.321 --> 38:16.080
If Father were here today,
would you dare to answer him like this?

38:16.520 --> 38:18.160
How dare you compare yourself to Father?

38:25.281 --> 38:27.881
(Xiuwen led the Heiyun Cavalry
into the capital without an edict.)

38:27.881 --> 38:30.321
(Cangbei seized the chance
and took three cities in a row.)

38:30.801 --> 38:32.881
(Yao, you were too impulsive.)

38:33.200 --> 38:36.080
(If you were still at Suixue Pass,
it wouldn't have come to this.)

38:46.080 --> 38:48.881
Your Highness, Her Highness
has set off for the Ye Mansion.

38:51.080 --> 38:53.680
Shall we still deliver
the prepared birthday gifts?

39:16.441 --> 39:18.361
Did you have a quarrel
with His Highness?

39:20.200 --> 39:21.640
Then why isn't he coming?

39:23.640 --> 39:26.001
Nothing of the sort.
Don't worry, Uncle Wenshen.

39:28.761 --> 39:30.361
It's good if you didn't quarrel.

39:31.720 --> 39:35.200
The way of husband and wife
is a profound art.

39:37.120 --> 39:40.001
You haven't even married yourself,
yet you know all this?

39:41.520 --> 39:43.921
One need not weave
to know the silkworm's work.

39:44.361 --> 39:46.441
I've managed the Longevity Shop
for so many years.

39:47.001 --> 39:50.001
I have contact with all the noble ladies
in the capital.

39:50.401 --> 39:52.361
I've heard so many boudoir secrets.

39:53.080 --> 39:54.720
Let me tell you, some families...

39:56.801 --> 39:57.761
It's indescribable.

39:59.961 --> 40:02.520
Li, you're already married now.

40:03.160 --> 40:06.441
In the future, you must,
amidst ordinary trivial matters,

40:06.441 --> 40:09.600
ponder more on the way
of husband and wife.

40:10.160 --> 40:14.120
It's not something those old tutors
at Lishan Mountain can teach you.

40:16.240 --> 40:20.200
Probing into others' private affairs
and citing it as personal experience?

40:20.640 --> 40:23.361
The tutors at Lishan Academy
indeed never taught me that.

40:24.200 --> 40:26.321
Your ability to apply knowledge
is truly impressive.

40:26.640 --> 40:29.761
If I remember correctly, you studied
under Master Xiankun, right?

40:32.120 --> 40:34.321
M-My master didn't teach me that.

40:34.321 --> 40:39.441
This... this is the worldly experience
from my early travels across the realm.

40:39.841 --> 40:40.801
Worldly experience.

40:44.321 --> 40:45.761
But anyway,

40:46.120 --> 40:49.441
if back then I hadn't left the mansion,

40:50.200 --> 40:53.801
I would never have let you
and your mom leave like that.

40:55.240 --> 40:57.841
People meet and part,
as the moon waxes and wanes.

40:58.600 --> 41:01.640
Fate rises and falls,
and it's only natural.

41:02.361 --> 41:05.361
I don't seek to force things.
You need not blame yourself.

41:09.881 --> 41:10.928
Mom!

41:13.040 --> 41:15.240
Mom! Mom!

41:16.560 --> 41:18.600
What's wrong? Wait for me.

41:21.321 --> 41:22.361
Mom!

41:22.720 --> 41:24.481
Mom? Mom?

41:24.481 --> 41:25.441
Mom, what's wrong?

41:25.680 --> 41:27.080
Don't scare me, Mom.

41:28.401 --> 41:30.281
Ding, stop the carriage.

41:37.200 --> 41:39.361
Hurry! Physician, please be faster!

41:41.881 --> 41:45.560
(Wenhua, give me back
the late emperor's decree! Give it back!)

41:45.560 --> 41:47.761
Let me go! Let me go!

41:47.761 --> 41:49.881
We'll doom Prince Ding's household!

41:51.160 --> 41:51.961
(Mom!)

41:52.560 --> 41:54.080
(Don't panic. Stay calm.)

41:54.080 --> 41:55.321
I will go find Father.

41:55.441 --> 41:57.080
I will retrieve the decree.

42:04.240 --> 42:06.160
(Some say that in the land of Xuanque,)

42:06.281 --> 42:07.761
(the sun will go out.)

42:08.761 --> 42:10.321
(But Mom once told me)

42:11.520 --> 42:13.520
(that the sun will never go out.)

42:15.160 --> 42:16.432
(It only sinks into the hearts)

42:17.361 --> 42:20.560
(of those who dare to warm
the long night with their chests.)

42:23.560 --> 42:25.441
Li, what's wrong?

42:25.441 --> 42:26.096
Your Highness?

42:26.520 --> 42:27.441
What happened?

42:27.441 --> 42:28.321
Why did you run?

42:28.560 --> 42:30.881
Come on. Let's go home.

42:32.921 --> 42:33.720
Wait.

42:36.080 --> 42:36.680
Take it.

42:36.961 --> 42:37.640
Li?

42:38.481 --> 42:39.281
What did you see?

42:40.803 --> 42:43.156
(Preview)

42:45.080 --> 42:46.040
You dare hit me?

42:46.441 --> 42:47.481
Why wouldn't I dare?

42:51.200 --> 42:52.321
I haven't hit you yet.

42:54.240 --> 42:54.841
Don't cry.

42:55.160 --> 42:55.761
Li,

42:56.761 --> 42:57.881
you must protect this well.

42:57.881 --> 42:58.600
Come with me.

42:59.281 --> 43:02.881
By doing this, you're making everyone
in the mansion die with you. Is that it?

43:03.441 --> 43:04.441
- Ye Wending!
- Go!

43:04.441 --> 43:05.680
Give me back the edict!

43:06.281 --> 43:07.040
Mom.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
